## 分页规范

禁止裸用 `<a-pagination>`，必须用 `table-card-cap` 结构：

```vue
<div class="zone-l4-table-card zone-card">
  <div class="table-card-cap">
    <div class="table-card-cap__left">
      <span class="table-card-cap__summary">共 <b>{{ page.total }}</b> 条</span>
    </div>
    <div class="table-card-cap__right">
      <a-pagination class="table-card-cap__pager"
        :current="page.current" :page-size="page.size" :total="page.total"
        :page-size-options="[50, 100, 200, 500]" size="small" show-page-size show-jumper
        @change="(p) => { page.current = p; fetchList(); }"
        @page-size-change="(s) => { page.size = s; fetchList(); }" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="table-wrap">
    <vxe-table ...>...</vxe-table>
  </div>
</div>
```

默认每页 100 条，page-size-options: [50, 100, 200, 500]

